comment: Generalization of ~ axsegcon . This time, we generate an endpoint for a segment on the ray ` Q A ` congruent to ` B C ` and starting at ` Q ` , as opposed to ~ axsegcon , where the segment starts at ` A ` (Contributed by Scott Fenton, 14-Oct-2013.) Remove unneeded inequality. (Revised by Scott Fenton, 15-Oct-2013.)
